history.proof: intros. intros y H2. destruct H2 as [H2 | H2]. - rewrite H2. apply in_eq. - apply in_cons. sfirstorder depth: 3.

exceptions.tactic: intros X x B A H1.
intros X' x B A H1.
intros X' x' B A H1.
intros X' x' B' A H1.
intros X' x' B' A' H1.

original: intros X x B A H1. intros y H2. destruct H2 as [H2 | H2]. - rewrite H2. apply in_eq. - apply in_cons. apply H1. apply H2.
